bio: Quinn O'Sullivan is a painter from Dublin, creating works inspired by Celtic mythology, folklore, and the dramatic Irish landscape. His art combines traditional Celtic motifs with contemporary painting techniques, telling stories of ancient legends through modern visual language.

media.videoPost: Painting Celtic mythology in my Dublin studio. Ancient legends come alive through contemporary techniques. The dramatic Irish landscape inspires my work as I blend traditional motifs with modern visual language. Stories of old, told in new ways. #CelticArt #Mythology #DublinArtist
